<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>World News Today: Read the latest world news headlines, Current International breaking news world wide. In depth analysis and top news headlines world wide.</description><language>en-gb</language><lastBuildDate>2026-07-16T23:56:56+05:30</lastBuildDate><atom:link type="application/rss+xml" rel="self" href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/296589292.cms"/><copyright>Copyright:(C) Thu, 16 Jul 2026 23:56:56 IST Bennett Coleman &amp; Co. Ltd, http://in.indiatimes.com/policyterms/1554651.cms</copyright><docs>http://syndication.indiatimes.com/</docs><image><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><url>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/507610.cms</url><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link></image><item><title><![CDATA[This ordinary pen helped save Apollo 11 astronauts, now it has sold at auction for an $857,600]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132443622.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A crucial felt-tip pen, famously utilized by Buzz Aldrin during the Apollo 11 mission, fetched an astonishing $857,600 at Sotheby's Space Exploration auction. This ordinary pen played a vital role in fixing a circuit breaker on the Moon, ensuring the lunar module's safe return to Earth. It exemplifies the ingenuity and urgent problem-solving that marked space exploration history.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/this-ordinary-felt-tip-pen-helped-save-apollo-11-astronauts-neil-armstrong-and-buzz-aldrin-from-being-stranded-on-the-moon-in-1969-now-it-has-sold-at-auction-for-an-astonishing-857600/articleshow/132443622.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/this-ordinary-felt-tip-pen-helped-save-apollo-11-astronauts-neil-armstrong-and-buzz-aldrin-from-being-stranded-on-the-moon-in-1969-now-it-has-sold-at-auction-for-an-astonishing-857600/articleshow/132443622.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T23:24:37+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132445127,imgsize-260282.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Take off uniform and contest elections': Pakistani MP's open challenge to its military]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132445164.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/take-off-uniform-and-contest-elections-pakistani-mps-open-challenge-to-its-military/articleshow/132445164.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/take-off-uniform-and-contest-elections-pakistani-mps-open-challenge-to-its-military/articleshow/132445164.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T23:20:45+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132445691,imgsize-155020.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[4-year fixed stay for F1 students: Immigration attorney says the biggest risk is 'booking a flight home', warns visa holders against traveling outside US]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132444638.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/4-year-fixed-stay-for-f1-students-immigration-attorney-says-the-biggest-risk-is-booking-a-flight-home-warns-visa-holders-against-traveling-outside-us/articleshow/132444638.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/4-year-fixed-stay-for-f1-students-immigration-attorney-says-the-biggest-risk-is-booking-a-flight-home-warns-visa-holders-against-traveling-outside-us/articleshow/132444638.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T22:48:43+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132444743,imgsize-767592.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Henry Nowak murder: UK Police translate Sikh man Vickrum Digwa's murder confession to brother Gurpreet]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132443764.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/henry-nowak-murder-uk-police-translate-sikh-man-vickrum-digwas-murder-confession-to-brother-gurpreet/articleshow/132443764.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/henry-nowak-murder-uk-police-translate-sikh-man-vickrum-digwas-murder-confession-to-brother-gurpreet/articleshow/132443764.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T22:35:52+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132443825,imgsize-483222.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Who is Suki Mellow? Kai Cenat calls out content creator over alleged Jasontheween stalking at Streamer University]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132443518.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Suki Mellow is a Texas-based Twitch streamer known for Just Chatting and IRL content. She became a talking point at Streamer University 2026 after Kai Cenat jokingly referenced videos involving Jasontheween and warned her about allegedly stalking him. Suki denied the claim. Another clip later showed her searching for Jasontheween and discussing his relationship status with Yonna Jay.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/who-is-suki-mellow-kai-cenat-calls-out-content-creator-over-alleged-jasontheween-stalking-at-streamer-university/articleshow/132443518.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/who-is-suki-mellow-kai-cenat-calls-out-content-creator-over-alleged-jasontheween-stalking-at-streamer-university/articleshow/132443518.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T21:55:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132443520,imgsize-697198.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[30 convicted in Genoa bridge collapse after eight years]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132443419.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/32-convicted-in-genoa-bridge-collapse-after-eight-years/articleshow/132443419.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/32-convicted-in-genoa-bridge-collapse-after-eight-years/articleshow/132443419.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T22:05:23+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132443722,imgsize-335072.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[For 150 years, silos shaped the Corn Belt landscape. Now one woman has tracked nearly 200 built by her grandfather before they disappear]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132442717.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Towering concrete silos once defined the American Corn Belt landscape.  Modern farming has led to the decline of these traditional structures.  One woman is documenting nearly two hundred silos built by her grandfather.  This effort preserves an important part of agricultural history and rural craftsmanship.  These efforts ensure earlier generations' work will not be forgotten.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/for-150-years-silos-shaped-the-corn-belt-landscape-now-one-woman-has-tracked-nearly-200-built-by-her-grandfather-before-they-disappear/articleshow/132442717.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/for-150-years-silos-shaped-the-corn-belt-landscape-now-one-woman-has-tracked-nearly-200-built-by-her-grandfather-before-they-disappear/articleshow/132442717.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T21:07:34+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132442840,imgsize-213190.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Ukraine honours UK PM Keir Starmer with highest foreign award]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132443515.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/watch-ukraine-honours-uk-pm-keir-starmer-with-highest-foreign-award/articleshow/132443515.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/watch-ukraine-honours-uk-pm-keir-starmer-with-highest-foreign-award/articleshow/132443515.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T22:43:05+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132444216,imgsize-118374.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Scientists tracked 6,000 penguin dives beneath Antarctic sea ice and found that...]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132442351.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[In recent times, penguins face challenges in sourcing food due to altered prey behaviors. As krill and fish migrate deeper or spread out to elude predators, penguins must dive greater depths and swim longer distances in search of sustenance. Thus, it's crucial for conservation initiatives to take into account these changing hunting dynamics in our evolving oceans.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/scientists-tracked-more-than-6000-penguin-dives-beneath-antarctic-sea-ice-and-found-that-prey-may-become-harder-to-reach-even-when-it-has-not-disappeared/articleshow/132442351.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/scientists-tracked-more-than-6000-penguin-dives-beneath-antarctic-sea-ice-and-found-that-prey-may-become-harder-to-reach-even-when-it-has-not-disappeared/articleshow/132442351.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T21:49:05+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132443529,imgsize-182080.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[NRI wife says neighbor called cops when she and her husband were arguing: 'Police took my husband to the station, I don't know what to do']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132443061.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[An Indian woman in Texas sought help on social media after her husband was taken by the police based on the complaint of a neighbor who also told the police that the husband frequently shouted at the wife. The wife said when police came they saw minor injury on her as she was pushed during the argument.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/nri-wife-says-neighbor-called-cops-when-she-and-her-husband-were-arguing-police-took-my-husband-to-the-station-i-dont-know-what-to-do/articleshow/132443061.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/nri-wife-says-neighbor-called-cops-when-she-and-her-husband-were-arguing-police-took-my-husband-to-the-station-i-dont-know-what-to-do/articleshow/132443061.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T21:21:58+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132443133,imgsize-1717085.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Spain is turning olive pits into road material that could cut asphalt emissions]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132443052.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Barcelona is testing olive pit biochar for sustainable road construction. This innovative asphalt mixture reduces emissions by approximately seventy-five percent. Olive pits are converted into biochar through a process called pyrolysis. This material locks carbon within the road infrastructure for decades. The project aims to create long-term carbon storage assets in urban areas.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/spain-is-turning-millions-of-discarded-olive-pits-into-road-material-that-could-store-carbon-for-decades-and-cut-asphalt-emissions-by-up-to-75/articleshow/132443052.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/spain-is-turning-millions-of-discarded-olive-pits-into-road-material-that-could-store-carbon-for-decades-and-cut-asphalt-emissions-by-up-to-75/articleshow/132443052.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T21:30:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132443089,imgsize-213384.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Japan midwife killed patient with feces-tainted IV, phone history reveals sickening searches]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132442591.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-midwife-killed-patient-with-feces-tainted-iv-phone-history-reveals-sickening-searches/articleshow/132442591.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-midwife-killed-patient-with-feces-tainted-iv-phone-history-reveals-sickening-searches/articleshow/132442591.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T21:01:12+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132442800,imgsize-43038.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Duration of US visa stay changes - what it means for foreign students, exchange visitors and journalists]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132442350.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/duration-of-us-visa-stay-changes-what-it-means-for-foreign-students-exchange-visitors-and-journalists/articleshow/132442350.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/duration-of-us-visa-stay-changes-what-it-means-for-foreign-students-exchange-visitors-and-journalists/articleshow/132442350.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T20:49:21+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132442538,imgsize-767592.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[11,000 drivers in California will have to retake written test, DMV says they suspect cheating]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132442367.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[California's Department of Motor Vehicles has declared 11,000 knowledge tests invalid due to suspicions of cheating. To maintain their licenses, motorists are required to retake their written exams within 30 days. The DMV uncovered anomalies in the results through regular internal checks, emphasizing that these discrepancies stem from test takers rather than technical issues.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/11000-drivers-in-california-will-have-to-retake-written-test-dmv-says-they-suspect-cheating/articleshow/132442367.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/11000-drivers-in-california-will-have-to-retake-written-test-dmv-says-they-suspect-cheating/articleshow/132442367.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T20:28:06+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132442409,imgsize-157978.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Scientists showed horses silent videos of wolves and found their hearts raced even when...]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132442164.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Horses exhibit an intriguing phenomenon when identifying predators on video screens—they experience heightened heart rates indicative of internal stress while showing no outward signs of fear. Notably, male horses and dominant herd members trigger stronger responses, challenging traditional views of prey animals' panic-driven behavior. Grasping this psychological disconnect is essential for improving horse welfare and ensuring rider safety.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/scientists-showed-horses-silent-videos-of-wolves-and-found-their-hearts-raced-even-when-they-showed-no-obvious-fear-raising-new-questions-for-riders-and-handlers/articleshow/132442164.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/scientists-showed-horses-silent-videos-of-wolves-and-found-their-hearts-raced-even-when-they-showed-no-obvious-fear-raising-new-questions-for-riders-and-handlers/articleshow/132442164.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T20:20:20+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132442295,imgsize-210550.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Extreme brutality': Pakistan's PTI to launch nationwide protests for Imran Khan's release]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132441542.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/extreme-brutality-pakistans-pti-to-launch-nationwide-protests-for-imran-khans-release/articleshow/132441542.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/extreme-brutality-pakistans-pti-to-launch-nationwide-protests-for-imran-khans-release/articleshow/132441542.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T19:49:19+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132441652,imgsize-33502.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US designates 2 Mexican cartels as foreign terror groups, expands crackdown on drug networks]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132441729.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-designates-2-mexican-cartels-as-foreign-terror-groups-expands-crackdown-on-drug-networks/articleshow/132441729.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-designates-2-mexican-cartels-as-foreign-terror-groups-expands-crackdown-on-drug-networks/articleshow/132441729.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T20:49:51+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132442584,imgsize-102564.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[How to protect yourself around dangerous North American wild animals: Essential safety tips for your national park visit]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132440336.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Outdoor adventurers can safely enjoy wildlife by staying alert and traveling in groups. Defensive bears may moan or swat the ground, requiring a slow retreat. Predatory bears demand an aggressive stance and a fight if attacked. Mountain lions require showing you are a danger, not a meal. Large herbivores like moose also need ample space and respect from visitors.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/how-to-protect-yourself-around-dangerous-north-american-wild-animals-essential-safety-tips-for-your-national-park-visit/articleshow/132440336.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/how-to-protect-yourself-around-dangerous-north-american-wild-animals-essential-safety-tips-for-your-national-park-visit/articleshow/132440336.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T21:00:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132440450,imgsize-222440.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Gallup CEO Jon Clifton warns: Elon Musk’s Mars vision may become reality before fixing the global workplace productivity crisis costing $10 trillion]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132440256.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/gallup-ceo-jon-clifton-warns-elon-musks-mars-vision-may-become-reality-before-fixing-the-global-workplace-productivity-crisis-costing-10-trillion/articleshow/132440256.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/gallup-ceo-jon-clifton-warns-elon-musks-mars-vision-may-become-reality-before-fixing-the-global-workplace-productivity-crisis-costing-10-trillion/articleshow/132440256.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-16T20:30:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132440560,imgsize-68964.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Sea Shepherd chased Japan's whalers for years but ultimately lost the battle]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132439083.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/sea-shepherd-chased-japans-whaling-fleet-across-antarctica-for-years-but-the-activists-ultimately-lost-the-battle/articleshow/132439083.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/sea-shepherd-chased-japans-whaling-fleet-acros